org.springframework.http.codec

类 AbstractServerHttpMessageReader<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.http.codec.AbstractServerHttpMessageReader<T>
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    HttpMessageReader<T>, ServerHttpMessageReader<T>
    直接已知子类:
    Jackson2ServerHttpMessageReader

    public abstract class AbstractServerHttpMessageReader<T>
extends Object
implements ServerHttpMessageReader<T>
    HttpMessageReader wrapper that implements ServerHttpMessageReader in order to allow providing hints to the nested reader or setting the response status for example, by implementing resolveReadHints(ResolvableType, ResolvableType, ServerHttpRequest).
    从以下版本开始:
    5.0
    作者:
    Sebastien Deleuze

        参数:

        read 在接口中 ServerHttpMessageReader<T>
        参数:
        streamType - the original type used in the method parameter. For annotation based controllers, the MethodParameter is available via ResolvableType.getSource().
        elementType - the stream element type to return Typically the value of a Content-Type header.
        request - the current HTTP request
        response - the current HTTP response
        hints - additional information about how to read the body
        返回:
        the converted Flux of elements
